0c24ae92cfab43c25a60c1f95e1ab6d72ca770c8f825b0a03c23&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\">运维苦，运维说说心底话</a>》\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	《<a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODYxMDA5OQ==&amp;mid=2651960095&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=227b8e3ee3027fcf2180fa12f771995e&amp;chksm=bd2d06c38a5a8fd58610bd771b18ddf257e14dc2248101b249ae59432ed257d4bbfd02f2efaf&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\">职场中的选择与拒绝</a>》\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	《<a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODYxMDA5OQ==&amp;mid=2651960162&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0a4814e76ae98f7b4597205bc9b4402c&amp;chksm=bd2d06be8a5a8fa8ea9cac53144d780160c853329af461b6ffa2d8002f93425c394140d1edb3&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\">罗振宇送给新员工的四句话</a>》\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	若有收获，帮忙<span style=\"color:#FF4C00;\">转发</span>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	下半年，继续上路，<strong>你的支持是我最大的动力</strong>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"></span> \r\n</p>', '', '', '5', '1506588083', '2017-09-28 16:41:23', '0', '1', '');
