INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('142', '48', '/upload/news/1709/201709300919263246.jpg', '奉节妇联开展“守护花季”主题法治巡讲暨中秋慰问活动', '李晓晓', '', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 44px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span>奉节县平安乡桃树小学和文昌小学地处奉节大山深处，交通十分不便，从县城去往学校需要3个半小时车程，桃树小学现有47名学生和5名教师，文昌小学有34名学生和4名教师。学校里面的孩子80%是留守儿童，父母长期在外务工，自我保护意识薄弱。针对这种情况，奉节县的“莎姐”检察官们给孩子们上了一堂生动的法治宣讲课。“莎姐”检察官给小朋友们发放了“莎姐”宣传手册，给小朋友们讲了如何预防身边的犯罪，教他们提高自身安全意识和技能。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 44px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span><img title=\"“莎姐”进行法制巡讲.jpg\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; max-width: 100%;\" alt=\"“莎姐”进行法制巡讲.jpg\" src=\"http://www.cqwomen.org.cn/Pic/20170929/15066727243323163.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 44px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span>“莎姐”进行法制巡讲</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 44px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span>在活动中，县妇联主席刘芳对每个孩子们提出要求，一是在家要孝顺父母，在学校尊重老师，热爱我们的家乡；二是要好好学习，知识改变命运，走出大山深处，努力成为社会精英；三是用积极的心态面对所处的困境，用勤劳的双手和聪明的智慧创造美好的生活。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 44px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span><img title=\"收到红包和月饼的孩子们.jpg\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; max-width: 100%;\" alt=\"收到红包和月饼的孩子们.jpg\" src=\"http://www.cqwomen.org.cn/Pic/20170929/15066727433781431.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 44px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span>收到红包和月饼的孩子们</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); text-transform: none; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 43px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span>通过开展“守护花季”主题法治巡讲暨中秋慰问活动，提高未成年人及其家长了解必要的预防性侵知识，引导家长切实履行监护责任，提高未成年人防范意识和能力。同时营造浓厚的节日氛围，温暖妇女儿童心田，及时把党和政府的关怀送到每一个慰问对象，确保他们过一个幸福、祥和的节日。</span></p><p></p>', 'https://v-cdn.zjol.com.cn/125347.mp4', 'http://api.yzhcb.com/uploadfile/2017/0903/20170928.mp3', '8', '1506734493', '2017-09-30 09:21:33', '0', '1', '');
